cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.AI 

The paper presents a framework for predicting tumor proliferation scores from breast histopathology whole slide images using image processing, deep learning, and prediction modules. This involves computer vision (cs.CV) techniques for image processing and mitosis detection, machine learning (cs.LG) for the prediction module, information retrieval (cs.IR) for handling the molecular data-based score, multimedia (cs.MM) for working with whole slide images, and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for the overall system design.
